{"ts": "2026-06-07T22:31:19.803240+00:00", "update": {"tools": {"messages": [{"type": "tool", "data": {"content": [{"type": "text", "text": "successfully downloaded text file (SHA: a0792bb3a5f4cb9f4a3c7df405a950368ed26fcd)", "id": "lc_b9a8461d-f37d-4618-96a6-b40389ac218c"}, {"type": "text", "text": "import React, { useState } from 'react';\nimport { Outlet } from 'react-router-dom';\nimport { styled } from '@mui/material/styles';\nimport DashboardNavbar from '@/layouts/dashboard/DashboardNavbar';\nimport DashboardSidebar from '@/layouts/dashboard/DashboardSidebar';\n\nconst APP_BAR_MOBILE = 64;\nconst APP_BAR_DESKTOP = 92;\n\nconst RootStyle = styled('div')({\n    display: 'flex',\n    minHeight: '100%',\n    overflow: 'hidden'\n});\n\nconst MainStyle = styled('div')(({ theme }) => ({\n    flexGrow: 1,\n    overflow: 'auto',\n    minHeight: '100%',\n    paddingTop: APP_BAR_MOBILE + 24,\n    paddingBottom: theme.spacing(10),\n    [theme.breakpoints.up('lg')]: {\n        paddingTop: APP_BAR_DESKTOP + 24,\n        paddingLeft: theme.spacing(2),\n        paddingRight: theme.spacing(2)\n    }\n}));\n\nconst DashboardLayout = () => {\n    const [open, setOpen] = useState(false);\n\n    return (\n        <RootStyle>\n            <DashboardNavbar onOpenSidebar={() => setOpen(true)} />\n            <DashboardSidebar isOpenSidebar={open} onCloseSidebar={() => setOpen(false)} />\n            <MainStyle>\n                <Outlet />\n            </MainStyle>\n        </RootStyle>\n    );\n};\n\nexport default DashboardLayout;\n", "id": "lc_db4f36bd-bcd3-4cb7-b0c8-a735d893c1ab"}], "additional_kwargs": {}, "response_metadata": {}, "type": "tool", "name": "get_file_contents", "id": "132fb3ed-5822-41f2-b29e-4681580da65e", "tool_call_id": "call_5b474ea7747b40ac860b1391", "artifact": null, "status": "success"}}]}}}
{"ts": "2026-06-07T22:31:19.840256+00:00", "update": {"tools": {"messages": [{"type": "tool", "data": {"content": [{"type": "text", "text": "successfully downloaded text file (SHA: 6d403ca09fc9222a52d3c2deafba257092a6a34b)", "id": "lc_89adb662-8faa-4035-9c8f-83aceee40ac3"}, {"type": "text", "text": "import React from 'react';\nimport { Icon } from '@iconify/react';\nimport pieChart2Fill from '@iconify/icons-eva/pie-chart-2-fill';\nimport peopleFill from '@iconify/icons-eva/people-fill';\nimport shoppingBagFill from '@iconify/icons-eva/shopping-bag-fill';\nimport fileTextFill from '@iconify/icons-eva/file-text-fill';\nimport lockFill from '@iconify/icons-eva/lock-fill';\nimport personAddFill from '@iconify/icons-eva/person-add-fill';\nimport alertTriangleFill from '@iconify/icons-eva/alert-triangle-fill';\nimport { NavItemConfig } from '@/models';\n\nconst getIcon = (name) => <Icon icon={name} width={22} height={22} />;\n\nconst sidebarConfig: NavItemConfig[] = [\n    {\n        title: 'dashboard',\n        path: '/dashboard/app',\n        icon: getIcon(pieChart2Fill)\n    },\n    {\n        title: 'user',\n        path: '/dashboard/user',\n        icon: getIcon(peopleFill)\n    },\n    {\n        title: 'product',\n        path: '/dashboard/products',\n        icon: getIcon(shoppingBagFill)\n    },\n    {\n        title: 'blog',\n        path: '/dashboard/blog',\n        icon: getIcon(fileTextFill)\n    },\n    {\n        title: 'login',\n        path: '/login',\n        icon: getIcon(lockFill)\n    },\n    {\n        title: 'register',\n        path: '/register',\n        icon: getIcon(personAddFill)\n    },\n    {\n        title: 'Not found',\n        path: '/404',\n        icon: getIcon(alertTriangleFill)\n    }\n];\n\nexport default sidebarConfig;\n", "id": "lc_b0a2e2a5-e685-4de1-9dba-75b208e1bda3"}], "additional_kwargs": {}, "response_metadata": {}, "type": "tool", "name": "get_file_contents", "id": "bdb8e3a6-6219-4a56-ab84-d1343ec6ae27", "tool_call_id": "call_3b67835b05ad4f0192790b05", "artifact": null, "status": "success"}}]}}}
{"ts": "2026-06-07T22:31:34.152671+00:00", "update": {"model": {"messages": [{"type": "ai", "data": {"content": "I now have a complete picture of the routing architecture. Here's a thorough explanation:\n\n---\n\n## Routing Architecture in `rpnr-bench/T02_R01_C02_A02`\n\n### Entry Point (`src/main.tsx`)\n\nThe app boots inside a `<BrowserRouter>` (React Router v6), wrapped by `HelmetProvider` (for `<head>` management), `ThemeConfig` (MUI theming), and a `<ScrollToTop>` utility. The top-level `<Router />` component (from `src/routes.tsx`) owns the entire route tree.\n\n---\n\n### Route Tree Overview (`src/routes.tsx`)\n\nThere are **two top-level route groups**, each using a different layout:\n\n```\n<Routes>\n  /dashboard/*  ──→  <DashboardLayout />     (sidebar + navbar shell)\n  /*            ──→  <LogoOnlyLayout />      (minimal shell: just a logo)\n</Routes>\n```\n\n---\n\n### 1. Dashboard Layout (`/dashboard/*`)\n\n**Layout component:** `src/layouts/dashboard/index.tsx`\n\nThis is the \"admin shell.\" It renders:\n- **`DashboardNavbar`** – a top app bar with a hamburger to open the sidebar, plus search/language/notification/account popovers.\n- **`DashboardSidebar`** – a collapsible side drawer whose nav items are defined in `SidebarConfig.tsx`.\n- **`<Outlet />`** – React Router renders the matched child route here.\n\n**Child routes under `/dashboard`:**\n\n| Path | Component | Notes |\n|---|---|---|\n| `/dashboard` (index) | `<Navigate to=\"/dashboard/app\">` | Bare `/dashboard` **redirects** to `/dashboard/app` |\n| `/dashboard/app` | `DashboardApp` | Main dashboard home (charts, summary cards) |\n| `/dashboard/user` | `User` | User management page |\n| `/dashboard/products` | `Products` | Product listing |\n| `/dashboard/blog` | `Blog` | Blog management |\n\nThe sidebar config (`SidebarConfig.tsx`) mirrors these paths as nav items with icons (pie chart, people, shopping bag, file text). It also includes convenience links to `/login`, `/register`, and `/404` for quick access during development.\n\n---\n\n### 2. LogoOnlyLayout (`/*` — the \"public\" shell)\n\n**Layout component:** `src/layouts/LogoOnlyLayout.tsx`\n\nThis is a **minimal, chrome-free layout** used for unauthenticated / standalone pages. It renders:\n- A **header** with just a clickable `<Logo />` (links back to `/`).\n- **`<Outlet />`** for the child page.\n\n**Child routes:**\n\n| Path | Component | Notes |\n|---|---|---|\n| `/login` | `Login` | Login page |\n| `/register` | `Register` | Registration page |\n| `/404` | `NotFound` (`Page404`) | Explicit 404 \"Not Found\" page |\n| `/` (index) | `<Navigate to=\"/dashboard\">` | Root URL **redirects** to the dashboard |\n| `*` (catch-all) | `<Navigate to=\"/404\">` | Any unmatched URL **redirects** to the 404 route |\n\n---\n\n### Redirects Summary\n\nThere are **three key redirect rules**:\n\n1. **`/` → `/dashboard`** — Hitting the app root bounces you into the dashboard (the `<Navigate>` under the `LogoOnlyLayout`'s index route).\n2. **`/dashboard` → `/dashboard/app`** — The bare dashboard path is never shown directly; it always redirects to the `app` sub-page.\n3. **`*` → `/404`** — Any URL that doesn't match a known route is caught by the wildcard under `LogoOnlyLayout` and redirected to `/404`.\n\n---\n\n### 404 / \"Not Found\" Behavior\n\nThe 404 flow is **redirect-based rather than rendered in-place**:\n\n1. An unknown URL (e.g. `/anything/unknown`) hits the `*` catch-all inside `LogoOnlyLayout`.\n2. That renders `<Navigate to=\"/404\" />`, causing a client-side navigation to `/404`.\n3. The `/404` path is an explicit `<Route>` that renders the `NotFound` component (`src/pages/Page404.tsx`).\n\nThis means the 404 page always gets its own clean URL (`/404`) rather than showing a \"Not Found\" message on an arbitrary URL. The `LogoOnlyLayout` shell keeps it visually consistent — logo on top, error content centered.\n\n---\n\n### Note on Auth\n\nThere is also a `src/layouts/AuthLayout.tsx` file in the layouts directory, but it is **not currently wired into the route tree**. The `Login` and `Register` pages are rendered inside `LogoOnlyLayout` rather than a dedicated auth layout. This suggests `AuthLayout` may be a leftover or reserved for future use (e.g., adding auth-specific chrome like \"forgot password\" links or social login branding).", "additional_kwargs": {"refusal": null}, "response_metadata": {"token_usage": {"completion_tokens": 1099, "prompt_tokens": 12661, "total_tokens": 13760, "completion_tokens_details": {"accepted_prediction_tokens": null, "audio_tokens": 0, "reasoning_tokens": 14, "rejected_prediction_tokens": null, "image_tokens": 0}, "prompt_tokens_details": {"audio_tokens": 0, "cached_tokens": 11776, "cache_write_tokens": 0, "video_tokens": 0}, "cost": 0, "is_byok": true, "cost_details": {"upstream_inference_cost": 0.0004645928, "upstream_inference_prompt_cost": 0.0001568728, "upstream_inference_completions_cost": 0.00030772}}, "model_provider": "openai", "model_name": "xiaomi/mimo-v2.5-20260422", "system_fingerprint": null, "id": "gen-1780871479-PfIy0VVkJZl0y7JjnWRv", "finish_reason": "stop", "logprobs": null}, "type": "ai", "name": null, "id": "lc_run--019ea436-4220-7683-b7ce-d29c20c5a978-0", "tool_calls": [], "invalid_tool_calls": [], "usage_metadata": {"input_tokens": 12661, "output_tokens": 1099, "total_tokens": 13760, "input_token_details": {"audio": 0, "cache_read": 11776}, "output_token_details": {"audio": 0, "reasoning": 14}}}}]}}}
